{"type": "article", "id": 25158, "title": "阿尔卑斯山半山腰的酒店，卖点还有无边界游泳池", "description": "无边界游泳池在山地环境中非常惬意。", "date": "2016-04-08T14:53:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 9, "name": "意大利"}, {"id": 13745, "name": "阿尔卑斯山"}, {"id": 667, "name": "酒店"}, {"id": 25992, "name": "Valentinerhof"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 545, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702131715kf5ZsqiMy1h9veCT.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.valentinerhof.com/en.html\">Valentinerhof </a>酒店坐落于阿尔卑斯山南侧意大利境内海拔 1200 米的地方，这里四周环绕着多罗迈特山，可以眺望对面 Schlern 雪山和自然植被分层后的山地景色，俯瞰 Bolzano 盆地低矮的农舍，周围不再有任何与城市有关的打扰，是隐藏在山间的度假型酒店。酒店距离 Seiser Alm 缆车有 3 公里，到了冬季则能聚集大量滑雪者。原本 20 个房间已不能满足当地繁荣的旅游业，他们邀请意大利的设计团队 noa*帮助扩建了酒店。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131701WD9XfgUB15Rc8jGl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75210084\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131702E4dTX9D0tAgVwuJi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>noa*在原有地址的东边重新修建了新建酒店是两幢相连的三层建筑，一共 1100 平方米的面积，包括大厅、游泳池、餐厅、健身房和 14 个套间。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>酒店依旧是沿着斜坡层层上升。他们想要建筑更融入当地的环境，则使用了石材墙面和木栅栏的结构。更特别在于一楼有一半的面积都在水中，建筑和前面的山地有一段河水，有野生的植物和石头。而在建筑的西侧即下图中的北边是一个 15 米宽的无边游泳池，游泳池的水一直流到日光浴甲板上，是非常惬意的晒太阳的地方。</p>\n<p>游泳池外用非常大的落地窗隔离室内室外，模糊了建筑、水和山区环境的边界，像是身处于自然中。远处的雪山景色和近处的水景分别是硬朗和柔和两种性格，这种反差也许能让人更加觉得特别。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317020RUmFdAHCTnNc5hQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39545455\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131703ui4sQjmMRcE1lKpa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131703g9n0J6UjzE3TaIic.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131704cpz731luLOeRdV4a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68541667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131704xUp8MCXm0gcuvP7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131705EwfCsF69GL8RjzpD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317050L8hot7BZg3bwur1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317068MDQdwmVZ5kgiT9F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131706puRK7r1Ij4qMxECk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131707UgWqE8pC2jkYLhci.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131707156ElzhxTtjq89UX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">一楼的桑拿房用了当地常用的木条作为室内装饰。房间与外面的河水相连，三面都环绕着落地玻璃，可以远眺周围的景色。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131707waieh3s612fIlzCG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67291667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131708E4ZOnCTHG2evtwfc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66737288\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131708zo3whmy2da5NsuMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66525424\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>房间集中在二、三楼，每层有 7 间，保证每个房间都正对着山谷并安装巨大的玻璃窗，非常明亮，可以一起床就看到自然景色。面对山谷的一侧是连通的走廊，中间用白色的 Heutücher 亚麻布作为隔断，使房间之间是相互打通的，倒是有一种轻松随意的气氛。</p>\n<p class=\"\">房间里的玻璃灯也是设计师自己设计的，他邀请罗马的玻璃吹制工共同完成，每盏都不一样。晶莹剔透的水珠的形状的灯串在一起，构成轻盈的点缀。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这家酒店房间价格夏季在 90 到 120 欧元之间，冬季每间要多出 20 欧元。这里是<a href=\"http://www.valentinerhof.com/en.html\">酒店链接</a>和<a href=\"http://www.booking.com/hotel/it/valentinerhof.zh-cn.html?label=gen173nr-1FCAsocUINdmFsZW50aW5lcmhvZkgzYgVub3JlZmgxiAEBmAEyuAEHyAEN2AEB6AEB-AELqAID;sid=33062b86d2fa83a3e83ffbe1984c5fad;dcid=12;checkin=2016-04-16;checkout=2016-04-17;dest_id=-129817;dest_type=city;dist=0;room1=A%2CA;sb_price_type=total;soldout=0%2C0;srfid=a05d239bd822431da82fc5671aa1608a0c0eac3aX1;type=total;ucfs=1&amp;\">预定链接</a>。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131709y61ZFnV7k4jsc8td.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317091vm50HFuaAVkxcb6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131710peJHI4bBn71XmA0o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68854167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131710vjy0WSUcfkGFCqLT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75210084\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317113zsuCPTJWUO9Yqd4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131711c5oqLbMEHNJKiYxr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131712Sj216ArLwKHlsWtZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.403125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131712OhE9pzAavymg7oNx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.42916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021317131APad7LK5oMw2Jim.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131713UfYDTsu6BieKtEFM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131714SVlrUJghnHGBWmdD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131714ZqkUDB61oFXfASNM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57916667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702131715NfqikmIWYs0uvAxO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.21458333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自</p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.booking.com/hotel/it/valentinerhof.zh-cn.html?label=gen173nr-1FCAsocUINdmFsZW50aW5lcmhvZkgzYgVub3JlZmgxiAEBmAEyuAEHyAEN2AEB6AEB-AELqAID;sid=33062b86d2fa83a3e83ffbe1984c5fad;dcid=12;checkin=2016-04-16;checkout=2016-04-17;dest_id=-129817;dest_type=city;dist=0;room1=A%2CA;sb_price_type=total;soldout=0%2C0;srfid=a05d239bd822431da82fc5671aa1608a0c0eac3aX1;type=total;ucfs=1&amp;\">booking</a>、<a href=\"http://www.valentinerhof.com/en.html\">Valentinerhof</a>、<a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/valentinerhof-silent-theater-schlern-by-noa.htm\">gooood</a></p>\n\n"}